HOW TO USE

import matplotlib_backend_fr.tk
import Tkinter
tk = Tkinter.Tk()
f = matplotlib_backend_fr.FigureAxes()
k = matplotlib_backend_fr.tk.KernelFigureAxes(tk, f)

Pan with left and right button on the figure.
Double-click left on the figure.
Double-click right on the figure.

For more info on how to instantiate FigureAxes, see source code.
